<topic id="xproc-transformation-scenario">
  <title>XProc Transformation</title>
  <!--Proofed-->
  <body>
    <p>A sequence of transformations described by an XProc script can be executed with an XProc
      transformation scenario. To create an <uicontrol>XProc transformation</uicontrol> scenario,
      use one of the following methods:<ul id="ul_fln_h5g_br">
        <li>Go to <menucascade>
            <uicontrol>Window</uicontrol>
            <uicontrol>Show View</uicontrol>
          </menucascade> and select <uicontrol><image href="../img/TransformConfig16.png"
              id="image_qvk_tvv_sr"/>Transformation Scenarios</uicontrol> to display this view.
          Click the <uicontrol>New</uicontrol> button and select <uicontrol>XProc
            transformation</uicontrol>.</li>
        <li>Use the <uicontrol><image href="../img/TransformConfig16.png" id="image_imp_tvv_sr"
            />Configure Transformation Scenario(s) (<shortcut
              conkeyref="reusable_oxygen_shortcuts_list/shortcut_ctrl_shift_c"
              product="author developer editor"/><shortcut
              conkeyref="reusable_oxygen_shortcuts_list/alt_shift_tc_shortcut"
              product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse"/>)</uicontrol> action from the
            <uicontrol>Transformation</uicontrol> toolbar or the <menucascade
            product="author developer editor">
            <uicontrol>Document</uicontrol>
            <uicontrol> Transformation</uicontrol>
          </menucascade><uicontrol product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse"
            >XML</uicontrol> menu. Then click the <uicontrol>New</uicontrol> button and select
            <uicontrol>XProc transformation</uicontrol>.</li>
        <li>Use the <uicontrol><image href="../img/ApplyStyleSheet16.png" id="image_vlr_4yv_sr"
            />Apply Transformation Scenario(s) (<shortcut
              conkeyref="reusable_oxygen_shortcuts_list/ctrl-shift-t-shortcut"
              product="author developer editor"/><shortcut
              conkeyref="reusable_oxygen_shortcuts_list/alt_shift_tt_shortcut"
              product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse"/>)</uicontrol> action from the
            <uicontrol>Transformation</uicontrol> toolbar or the <menucascade
            product="author developer editor">
            <uicontrol>Document</uicontrol>
            <uicontrol> Transformation</uicontrol>
          </menucascade><uicontrol product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse"
            >XML</uicontrol> menu. Then click the <uicontrol>New</uicontrol> button and select
            <uicontrol>XProc transformation</uicontrol>.<note id="note-001">If a scenario is already
            associated with the edited document, selecting <uicontrol><image
                href="../img/ApplyStyleSheet16.png" id="image_eqv_4yv_sr"/>Apply Transformation
              Scenario(s)</uicontrol> runs the associated scenario automatically. You can check
            whether transformation scenarios are associated with the edited document by hovering
            your cursor over the <uicontrol><image href="../img/ApplyStyleSheet16.png"
                id="image_hj2_pyv_sr"/>Apply Transformation Scenario</uicontrol> button.
          </note></li>
      </ul></p>
    <p>All three methods open the <uicontrol>New Scenario</uicontrol> dialog box. This dialog box
      allows you to configure the options that control the transformation.</p>
    <p conref="xml-transformation-with-xslt.dita#xml-transformation-with-xslt/name-storage-options"/>
    <p>The lower part of the dialog box contains the following tabs:<ul>
        <li><xref href="xproc-transformation-xproc-tab.dita#xproc-transformation-xproc-tab"
              ><uicontrol>XProc</uicontrol></xref></li>
        <li><xref href="xproc-transformation-inputs-tab.dita#xproc-transformation-inputs-tab"
              ><uicontrol>Inputs</uicontrol></xref></li>
        <li><xref
            href="xproc-transformation-parameters-tab.dita#xproc-transformation-parameters-tab"
              ><uicontrol>Parameters</uicontrol></xref></li>
        <li><xref href="xproc-transformation-outputs-tab.dita#xproc-transformation-outputs-tab"
              ><uicontrol>Outputs</uicontrol></xref></li>
        <li><xref href="xproc-transformation-options-tab.dita#xproc-transformation-options-tab"
              ><uicontrol>Options</uicontrol></xref></li>
      </ul></p>
  </body>
